snippet.title: FreshandFit
snippet.description:
Welcome to FreshandFit where we provide the TRUTH to Fitness, Finances, and Women. We help men with self improvement. 

We will teach you how to fully optimize the dating market by specifying topics that relate to female psychology, dating apps, style, photography, and how to market yourself to women.

Myron Gaines will teach you how to build an aesthetic physique by teaching you NO BS tactics that the fitness industry REFUSES to tell you with evidence based research.

Subscribe for FREE DAILY videos on Money Mondays, Womanizer Wednesdays, and Fitness Fridays at 7pm. 

On Mon-Fri, at 10pm we have Fresh&Fit AfterHours where we bring panels of different girls EVERY NIGHT so you can see how modern women view dating and see the TRUTH. 

Send Collaboration / Sponsorship Requests to: 
freshfitpodcast@gmail.com or DM @Freshfitpodcast on Instagram.
